Over the years I have developed such a good relationship towards food. I see it as the building blocks for my body to heal, grow and strengthen over time. 🍀Hand in hand with that goes my oral care which is also a very important part of my lifestyle. I always brush twice a day and make sure my teeth and gums stay in optimal condition. I brush my tongue to get rid of bacteria that has build up because of the food I ate, so I know for sure my teeth stay as healthy as the rest of my body😄👍🏽 Fun fact: I haven’t had any cavities the last few years👀 Let’s keep it that way hihi🙆🏻‍♀️♥️ #newcolgatetotal #interdentalclean #gezondemond
